    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a canonical address format encoding used in
   Locator/ID Separation Protocol (LISP) control messages and in the
   encoding of lookup keys for the LISP Mapping Database System.

   This document obsoletes RFC 8060 and RFC 9306.</t>
    </abstract>
